Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:45.10,Note,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「……」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:37.48,NoteV,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\pos(1500,112.5)}五年三班\N\N八九寺真宵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:57.18,Note,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿良良木君你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.88,0:18:24.38,Note,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}八九寺真宵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:51.87,Note,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I LOVE YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.48,0:19:20.69,Note,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「……哎？」
